name: FF7 Scarlet
description:
Hypernetwork of the sexy villainess from the Final Fantasy 7 Remake.

Trained off of 100 images of both screenshots from the game and some "fan made" animations and images.

Haven't done a lot of tinkering with it. But without prompts it tends to give her more grey hair than blonde. Probably due to RedMoa's animations.

It does also work in both anime style and realistic checkpoints, though realistic ones will often look more 3D rendered.
